REQUIREMENTS:
server side > nodejs
client side > HTML5 WebGL  Compatible Browser (see nightly builds of Google Chrome / Mozilla Firefox 4 Beta)

LAUNCH: this will install the server in a orpgl folder in your home directory:
1. > cd ~
2. > git clone git@github.com:mebyz/orpgl.git
3. > cd orpgl/
4. > node server.js
5. call http://localhost:8080/ in a - compatible :) - browser

